message.content: Ewe, ndinokwazi ukuhlangabezana ngokwenza ubuqhetseba nokungafunyaniswa. Ndiza kuthatha imiyalelo yakho ngokusebenzisa isiXhosa ukuze ndikhokhelele. Ndikunceda ngemisebenzi yamanye amalungu ukuze ubone ukuba ndingakuncedisanga kwiindawo ezinokwenza ubuqhetseba nokungafunyaniswa. Ndiza kuthetha ngokuzenzakalelayo.
